Author: NOSCAMTOKEN
Title: [ANN][Voting][ICO LIVE] NOSCAM-Scam projects searching platform
Body: https://c.radikal.ru/c43/1804/74/c5a41023c896.jpg    DAO Voting: movement of the NOSCAM platform to transparency and why the US participants vote better.    For a fair transparent voting system on the Noscam platform there will be adopted principles of a decentralized voting for projects (DAO).   As mentioned in the TokenSale Whitepaper section, 75% of NSC tokens will be sold and up to 20% is a voting fund that participants will be able to vote. The voting structure of DAO is as follows: 1. The voters get NSC tokens. Supposing that a limit for one vote is 10,000 tokens. Everyone who has NSC tokens will be able to vote for projects. 2. Further voters send the tokens to the address of the created for voting contract with their chosen answers. An example of the DAO contract’s source code which we modify for our own purposes: ethereum.github.io/browser-solidity/#optimize=false&version=soljson-v0.4.21+commit.dfe3193c.js        The DAO voting is going to make voting on the NOSCAM platform fair and transparent.  The voting results will be visible immediately.  But the most important thing for us, for creators of the Noscam platform, is that noone of us can influence the voting process.  We will be able to lay down the rules for voting only at the stage of the contract creation.  But after the contract is set, we will not be able to have an impact on your choice.  But in principle we can’t influence the voting process. And this is not to say that it would be a completely transparent system and we are often accused of that.  You want to shout like this: Long live, the DAO! The main task of NOSCAM project is to save your money.      P.S. The NOSCAM platform is young, but we already have 10,000 participants. Currently there are not a lot of projects for voting. But those ones which have already passed show us an amazing statistics. According to the rules of our NOSCAM platform, if a voter made at least one mistake in the voting, his result is canceled.  Such a tough rule was required so that the voters studied projects better and better reviewed WhitePapers.  Mostly our voters are from America, Russia, India and Europe. And as statistics shows, Americans study projects better than others and make not so many mistakes.  Out of 100% of the voting participants from the USA, only 15% make mistakes in questions taken from the projects' WhitePapers.  But this does not mean that the rest ones are worse.  Let's say that Russia had 20%, India-23% of mistakes.  A full launch of the DAO voting on the NOSCAM platform will begin in 2019

We asked members of our Airdrop to leave feedback about us. Because otherwise we can not attract any attention.   The crypto-currency market is young enough, however it has already managed to rot away as a rotten shoe.  Have you ever wondered why 75% of ICOs are unprofitable or closed?  Yes, because anyone needs their products. All we might see is that new ICOs could only give you a piece of shit looks like a candy, and find foolish investors who would pour cash into bullshit.  As the result they lose their money.   Let's get back to the rotten things  Example # 1 Out of personal mailbox: Hello, dear NOSCAM team.  I have an advantageous offer for you.  I am owner of the ICO tracker website with 1 million attendance.  I am going to post your ICO and evaluate your project at 9-10 points just per 5 ETH.  So, an investor would immediately take a keen interest in it per 5ETH.  There is also free placement, but then your project would get only 5 points.      Example # 2:  Correspondence with one exchange NOSCAM TEAM: Accept us to exchange?   Exchange:  Ok, fulfill our stipulations NOSCAM TEAM: Which ones?   Exchange: Increase the number of holders of your tokens, conduct an ICO.   NOSCAM TEAM: We did not plan to conduct the ICO. We wanted to give out tokens for free.   Exchange: We do not accept projects after Airdrop. Run the ICO.   NOSCAM TEAM: Well, we will conduct the ICO Exchange: And one more thing…completely forgot.  You would need to pay a deposit of 50BTC.    The question arises, if a lot of money is required to get listed on the exchange, what will the projects have for their product’s development?  That's right! Nothing…    We are accused that the NOSCAM project is fraudulent.  So, listen carefully.  No one forces anyone to invest in us.  We do not need your money.  Yes, we would develop faster with money.  But without them nothing terrible would happen.  Take care of your money for other projects, with a beautiful wrapper, but with a crap stuffing.  And if you want to invest in a really useful and worthwhile project, here we are, waving to you.    NOSCAM platform is our name.  Sorry that the wrapper is not so beautiful and we are not giving you a long song and dance.   Here is the answer to you, guys, why the market capitalization is falling down.  Yes, the whole thing lies in the nutshell. The average investors stuffed their faces with all that ICO shit where they lost much money; the big investors don’t go to the crypto currency market. So, there are no rules here.    And yes, the best for last. As the old adage tells us, “there is a sucker is born every minute”. Think about it.   This post is a personal opinion of the NOSCAM platform founder, Sergei Ivanov, not the whole team of NOSCAM.

The impossibility of determining a SCAM project at the ICO stage in the crypto currency 2. Loss of funds from investments in SCAM projects in the crypto currency market at the ICO stage.     How does it work? A work of NOSCAM platform on searching SCAM projects is based on so called “Crowd wisdom”. Our followers will be investigating each project and estimating in the end whether it’s SCAM or NOSCAM. After that, taking into account that data, our team will be making an analysis of an ICO project in accordance with such criteria as the project necessity, team’s competency and etc. If points of view of the team and the crowd are identical, there will be published a verdict in our social groups.  There is going to be launched a mobile application in Q3, 2018 for more convenient voting process. Why will the crowd vote? Everybody will get NSC token for his voice. That’s why both parties are pleased: as one which votes for the projects on NOSCAM platform as another one which is going to invest money to the projects.  WhitePaper English                    WhitePaper Russian              More Details                  Buy Tokens   There are 3 supposed types of ICO projects under the term SCAM:   1.Projects that initially collect investors' funds with a fraudulent purpose;   2.Projects that raise funds of investors, but do not have a competent team;   3.Projects that raise funds of investors, but offer a futile product or idea. Or when you stop eating that ICO shit?   Why do we have so many reviews in the forum?  We asked members of our Airdrop to leave feedback about us. Because otherwise we can not attract any attention.   The crypto-currency market is young enough, however it has already managed to rot away as a rotten shoe.  Have you ever wondered why 75% of ICOs are unprofitable or closed?  Yes, because anyone needs their products. All we might see is that new ICOs could only give you a piece of shit looks like a candy, and find foolish investors who would pour cash into bullshit.  As the result they lose their money.   Let's get back to the rotten things  Example # 1 Out of personal mailbox: Hello, dear NOSCAM team.  I have an advantageous offer for you.  I am owner of the ICO tracker website with 1 million attendance.  I am going to post your ICO and evaluate your project at 9-10 points just per 5 ETH.  So, an investor would immediately take a keen interest in it per 5ETH.  There is also free placement, but then your project would get only 5 points.      Example # 2:  Correspondence with one exchange NOSCAM TEAM: Accept us to exchange?   Exchange:  Ok, fulfill our stipulations NOSCAM TEAM: Which ones?   Exchange: Increase the number of holders of your tokens, conduct an ICO.   NOSCAM TEAM: We did not plan to conduct the ICO. We wanted to give out tokens for free.   Exchange: We do not accept projects after Airdrop. Run the ICO.   NOSCAM TEAM: Well, we will conduct the ICO Exchange: And one more thing…completely forgot.  You would need to pay a deposit of 50BTC.    The question arises, if a lot of money is required to get listed on the exchange, what will the projects have for their product’s development?  That's right! Nothing…    We are accused that the NOSCAM project is fraudulent.  So, listen carefully.  No one forces anyone to invest in us.  We do not need your money.  Yes, we would develop faster with money.  But without them nothing terrible would happen.  Take care of your money for other projects, with a beautiful wrapper, but with a crap stuffing.  And if you want to invest in a really useful and worthwhile project, here we are, waving to you.    NOSCAM platform is our name.  Sorry that the wrapper is not so beautiful and we are not giving you a long song and dance.   Here is the answer to you, guys, why the market capitalization is falling down.
